short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sun-Panel is a homepage of NAS, servers, and browsers that support self-hosting.This is the browser auxiliary plugin of Sun-Panel.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sun Panel BE can set any address as a new tab page for the browser. At the same time, when paired with a self built Sun Panel, it is also possible to quickly add icon cards to the Sun Panel.
